     <p class="B1SpeakersName"><strong>Mr F McCann</strong>:  Go raibh maith agat, a Cheann Comhairle. Community heating systems have been  successful in Scandinavia, particularly in Denmark where more than half of all  homes are heated through such schemes. What discussion has the Minister had  with the Minister for Social Development about developing such an  infrastructure here? What support has the Department of Enterprise, Trade and  Investment given to companies here that want to develop community heating  systems?</p>
